getOrbitPositions

public java.util.ArrayList<PVector> getOrbitPositions(java.util.Date refDate,
                                                      int res,
                                                      int minutesBefore,
                                                      int minutesAfter)
A method to return an ArrayList of "PVector" positions(x,y,z) from minutesBefore the reference date to minutesAfter.

Parameters:
Date - refDate the reference Date, can be the present date or a date in the past or future
int - res Resolution, or increment rate to generate predictions (tricky to define, but it should be kept low, specially for long time spans)
int - minutesBefore Used to define a date in the past, substracting minutes to the refDate. Pass 0 if it must be the same refDate
int - minutesAfter Used to define a date in the future, adding minutes to the refDate. Pass 0 if it must be the same refDate

getOrbitAsCoordinates

public java.util.ArrayList<PVector> getOrbitAsCoordinates(java.util.Date refDate,
                                                          int res,
                                                          int minutesBefore,
                                                          int minutesAfter)
A method to return an ArrayList of "PVector" coordinates (lat,lon) from minutesBefore the reference date to minutesAfter.

Parameters:
Date - refDate the reference Date, can be the present date or a date in the past or future
int - res Resolution, or increment rate to generate predictions (tricky to define, but it should be kept low, specially for long time spans)
int - minutesBefore Used to define a date in the past, substracting minutes to the refDate. Pass 0 if it must be the same refDate
int - minutesAfter Used to define a date in the future, adding minutes to the refDate. Pass 0 if it must be the same refDate
